{
  "stem": "25381.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he took with a gun and he shot her straight in the head.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And her meat in the head and everything was on the-- on the windowsills, on the wall, on the floor, all over the pieces.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He shot her right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That means, damn it, I shot at her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I turned right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That-- you know, he did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That mean, [NON-ENGLISH]-- that means, I killed her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That he was timing, and it was OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had to-- all over, the hand, the floor, the walls was all over, you know with-- full of blood, and full of meat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The eyes and the head cut in half all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to clean, us girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to clean.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We started screaming and shouting and crying, terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We became very emotional.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And her parents came over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They called right away the parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was hysterical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said, if you're not going to shut your mouth, you're going to be killed right away, all of you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then within a week later, I went again to wash the floor, to work over there and to-- to wash the floor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to carry the pails with water from far away from the well and we had some brooms.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it's not like here that you have carpeting, you have a sweeper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You had to wash with your-- with your-- on the knees with a-- with a pail with water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And to scrub with a broom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then he tried to kill me, to put the bullet towards me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And instead, I didn't even realize.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I stood by the window so another boy, not the same.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And instead, the bullet to go into me-- I didn't even realize.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
